<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.8">
<l>iṅkē pōtuṅkolō</l>
<l>viṉavēlneṭuṅ kaṇkaḷippa</l>
<l>koṅkār cōlai<supplied>k</supplied>ku ṭantai<supplied>k</supplied>ki  ṭantamāl</l>
<l>iṅkē pōtuṅkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will he come here?</l>
<l>So that my long, eyes [like] a set of lances reel,</l>
<l>Māl who sleeps in Kuṭantai with nectar-filled groves</l>
<l>Will he come here?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
